  "detailed_description": "Do you like Sports? Do you really, really like sports? Enough to date one of them? No?... Well.. this is awkward. If you change your mind, oh boy we have the game for you.<br><br><strong>Do you need to know something about sports to play this game?</strong><br>Of course not! This is just a funny game that makes fun of pop culture. If you know how to read you are overqualified.<br><br>Live your best scholar life and date 7 amazing and not insane characters, while you try to become the next big sport that will take over the world (preferable by non violent means, but don't discard anything yet).<br>Each character has Two endings and a lot of side routes/content and minigames. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521490/extras/45021d05231e965dd46100e3861192b8.poster.avif?t=1732029934\" width=568 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521490/extras/45021d05231e965dd46100e3861192b8.webm?t=1732029934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521490/extras/45021d05231e965dd46100e3861192b8.mp4?t=1732029934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521490/extras/01d59dd14cad4f1fc7217f81911d9307.poster.avif?t=1732029934\" width=574 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521490/extras/01d59dd14cad4f1fc7217f81911d9307.webm?t=1732029934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521490/extras/01d59dd14cad4f1fc7217f81911d9307.mp4?t=1732029934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video cl